    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="下载-idm"><a href="#下载-idm" class="headerlink" title="下载 idm"></a>下载 idm</h1><ul><li>首先从官网下载IDM并安装：<a href="https://www.internetdownloadmanager.com/">https://www.internetdownloadmanager.com</a><br>![1](<a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/屏幕截图</a> 2023-12-30 112525.png)</li><li>建议安装在 c 盘，要不然 IE 浏览器可能加载不了扩展<br>![2](<a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/屏幕截图</a> 2023-12-30 112743.png)<br>安装完成后可以看到 EDGE 扩展里已经自动装上去了<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/idm" alt="3"></li></ul><h1 id="下载-idm-激活工具"><a href="#下载-idm-激活工具" class="headerlink" title="下载 idm 激活工具"></a>下载 idm 激活工具</h1><p>下载后解压，并运行 IAS_0.8_cn.cmd<br>输入 3 先把防火墙关了，出现 disabled 就是已经处于关闭状态<br>![4](<a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/屏幕截图</a> 2023-12-30 124419.png)<br>接着输入 1 激活 idm 即可<br>等程序跑完之后打开 idm 点击 注册，发现<strong>本软件已注册</strong><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/20231230125052.png" alt="5"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0730aa/images/remain/2023/December/20231230125111.png" alt="6"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
