    <published>2023-12-23T12:39:47.885Z</published>
    <updated>2023-12-25T16:00:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="docker-执行命令"><a href="#docker-执行命令" class="headerlink" title="docker 执行命令"></a>docker 执行命令</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run --name geminiprochat \</span><br><span class="line">--restart always \</span><br><span class="line">-p 3030:3000 \</span><br><span class="line">-itd \</span><br><span class="line">-e GEMINI_API_KEY=你的api值 \</span><br><span class="line">howie6879/geminiprochat:v0.1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>直接把上面的代码复制到已经安装 docker 的机器<br>记得在服务器配置放行 3030 端口</li></ol><ul><li>如果你是国内服务器搭建，则搭建完成后访问会出现访问失败等情况，如下<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/0730aa/images/20231223203838.png" alt="1"></li></ul><h1 id="效果图"><a href="#效果图" class="headerlink" title="效果图"></a>效果图</h1><ul><li>只有国外服务器才可以返回数据，国内不行<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/0730aa/images/20231223204257.png" alt="2"></li></ul><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/0730aa/images/20231226115525.png" alt="3"></p><ul><li>不过目前体验还是不友好，返回还有乱码</li><li>推荐先使用 bard 或者 使用网页版的 Gemini pro<br>bard：<a href="https://bard.google.com/chat/6d9823bd666ad17e">https://bard.google.com/chat/6d9823bd666ad17e</a><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/0730aa/images/20231226120554.png" alt="4"><br>Gemini pro：<a href="https://makersuite.google.com/app/prompts/new_freeform">https://makersuite.google.com/app/prompts/new_freeform</a><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/0730aa/images/20231226120931.png" alt="5"></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
